    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let the dark spells take care of your character and give him power! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As part of this set, you will find:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297150/extras/0df5783df7d9ee5d9143350fbdbf8f9a.webp?t=1743694052\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Stability Powder R.7 (1 piece) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This powder will protect the item from breakage when enchanted. If the enchantment fails, the enchantment level does not change. Disappears with successful and unsuccessful enchantment.</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297150/extras/1f06650c3845eff57b866ea42061cb3c.webp?t=1743694052\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Recovery Powder (1 piece) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The powder helps to restore a thing that was broken during an unsuccessful charm. When restoring an item, the enchantment level is 50%.</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297150/extras/6f188fd44fac22d383c6098d1f5c16af.webp?t=1743694052\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Unstable essence of the Soul Stone (5 pieces) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Allows you to enhance the improved soul stones from +5 to +10 from the Energy Master</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297150/extras/5f1748e8f7e5c051a87f981bdb7bc051.webp?t=1743694052\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Dark Forces Wallet (1 piece) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>When equipping this item, the character receives an aura that increases the character's characteristics.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297150/extras/048dc5f44d184098005d6ad28b8bd732.webp?t=1743694052\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Potion of Random Skill Changes (1 piece)  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A potion that resets random character skills</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297150/extras/7f59041351810f2763d63e74b9c7da56.webp?t=1743694052\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Fairy Goddess Bottle [NP] (10 pcs)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Allows you to resurrect yourself without losing experience. You can revive yourself without help. The lost experience is fully restored.</i></p>",
